Class SystemPropertiesConfigSource

java.lang.Object
  com.netflix.florida.AbstractConfigSource
      com.netflix.florida.SystemPropertiesConfigSource
All Implemented Interfaces:
IConfigSource
public final class SystemPropertiesConfigSource
extends AbstractConfigSource

Loads System.getProperties() as a source.

Implementation note: set(String, String) does not write to system properties, but will write to a new map. This means that setting values to this source has no effect on system properties or other instances of this class.
